# Code Structure Guidelines

## Technology Stack
- Next.js como framework principal
- Tailwind CSS para estilos
- shadcn/ui para componentes de UI
- InstantDB para capa de datos

## Directory Organization
- Page components go in `app/`
- Reusable components go in `components/`
- Utilities and hooks go in `lib/`
- Data layer code goes in `db/`

## Clean Code Principles
- No barrel files (index.ts)
- Import directly from source files
- Avoid obvious or redundant comments
- Comments should only explain complex logic or non-evident decisions
- No TODOs or incomplete code in production

## Component Guidelines
- Keep components small and focused
- Use Tailwind CSS directly in components
- Follow shadcn/ui installation and usage patterns